'''兵工厂委员会'''（简称OFB）是由41家兵工厂组成的[[印度|印度]]国有军工[[托拉斯|托拉斯]]<ref name="OFB Brief">{{cite web|url=https://www.ofb.gov.in/pages/ofb-in-brief|title=OFB in Brief - Ordnance Factory Board|publisher=Ordnance Factory Board|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029053849/https://www.ofb.gov.in/pages/ofb-in-brief|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ofb.gov.in/pages/ofb-in-brief|title=Our Units - Ordnance Factory Board|publisher=Ordnance Factory Board|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029053849/https://www.ofb.gov.in/pages/ofb-in-brief|dead-url=no}}</ref>，总部设在[[加尔各答|加尔各答]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/Factories+of+graft/1/47422.html|title=Factories of graft|publisher=|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224202959/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/Factories+of+graft/1/47422.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>拥有超过200年的兵工生产历史。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mod.nic.in/product&supp/welcome.html |title=Ministry of Defence, Govt of India |publisher=Mod.nic.in |accessdate=2012-07-17 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704170459/http://mod.nic.in/product%26supp/welcome.html |archivedate=2012-07-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/of.htm|title=Ordnance Factories|author=John Pike|publisher=|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-date=2019-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024175344/https://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/of.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>隶属于[[印度国防部|印度国防部]]的国防生产部（department of defence production）。每年3月18日为印度的兵工厂日（Ordnance Factory Day）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehitavada.com/news-details/vfj-celebrates-212th-ordnance-factory-day|title=VFJ celebrates 212th Ordnance Factory Day|publisher=The Hitavada|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703090103/http://www.thehitavada.com/news-details/vfj-celebrates-212th-ordnance-factory-day|archive-date=2015-07-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="thehindubusinessline1">{{cite web |author=Our Bureau |url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/article3017269.ece |title=Business Line : Industry & Economy News : Ordnance Factory to invest Rs 15,000 cr for modernisation |publisher=Thehindubusinessline.com |date= |accessdate=2012-07-17 |archive-date=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429075959/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/article3017269.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年OFB军工销售额为26.5亿美元，占总销售额的96%，位居全球军工百强第37位，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ofb.gov.in/pages/about-us |title=About Us - Ordnance Factory Board |publisher=Ordnance Factory Board |accessdate=2012-07-17 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031020351/https://ofb.gov.in/pages/about-us |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://hal-india.com/othermod.asp|title=Page Not Found|publisher=|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114173543/http://hal-india.com/othermod.asp|archive-date=2014-11-14|url-status=dead|dead-url=no}}</ref>员工总数164,000人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mod.nic.in/Samachar/april15-02/html/ch1.htm |title=Two Centuries of Guns and Shells |publisher=Mod.nic.in |accessdate=2012-07-17 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207204324/http://mod.nic.in/Samachar/april15-02/html/ch1.htm |archivedate=2012-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiadefence.com/OFB.htm|title=WHAT|publisher=|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924034309/http://www.indiadefence.com/OFB.htm|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ofbgcf.nic.in/default.html|title=Gun Carriage Factory|publisher=|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213735/http://ofbgcf.nic.in/default.html|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
==历史==
印度最早的兵工厂是1712年{{tsl|en|Ostend Company|由奥地利皇帝特许的东印度总公司}}在[[西孟加拉|西孟加拉]]的{{tsl|en|Ichhapur}}建立的炮药工厂<ref name="ofbindia.gov.in">{{Cite web|url=http://ofbindia.gov.in/download/pr/december2006.pdf|title=404 | Ordnance Factory Board | Government of India|website=ofbindia.gov.in|accessdate=2020-12-06|archive-date=2019-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024181337/https://ofbindia.gov.in/download/pr/december2006.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1775年在加尔各答的[[威廉堡_(印度)|威廉堡]]建立了兵工委员会。1787年，在{{tsl|en|Ichhapur}}建立了另一家火药厂，1791年开始生产，1904年改为来复枪厂。1801年在加尔各答的{{tsl|en|Cossipore}}建立了“Gun Carriage Agency”(现称 Gun & Shell Factory, Cossipore) ，1802年3月18日投产。这是印度现存最古老的兵工厂。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ofb.gov.in/units/index.php?unit=gsf&page=about&lang=en |title=Indian Ordnance Factories: Gun and Shell Factory |publisher=Ofb.gov.in |date= |accessdate=2012-07-17 |archive-date=2016-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313053622/http://ofb.gov.in/units/index.php?lang=en&page=about&unit=gsf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

兵工系统建立了印度第一家现代钢铁厂<ref name="ReferenceA">{{Cite web | url=http://ofbindia.gov.in/units/index.php?unit=msf&page=about&lang=en | title=Indian Ordnance Factories: Metal and Steel Factory | accessdate=2020-12-06 | archive-date=2018-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715093842/http://ofbindia.gov.in/units/index.php?unit=msf&page=about&lang=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>、第一家现代纺织厂、第一家现代化学厂生产无烟发射药<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://ofbindia.gov.in/units/index.php?unit=cfa&page=about&lang=en | title=Indian Ordnance Factories: Cordite Factory Aruvankadu | accessdate=2020-12-06 | archive-date=2017-03-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170328101754/http://ofbindia.gov.in/units/index.php?unit=cfa&page=about&lang=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>、第一家工科高等学校<ref name="educationforallinindia.com">{{Cite web |url=https://www.educationforallinindia.com/1949%20Report%20of%20the%20University%20Education%20Commission.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-12-06 |archive-date=2018-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180329064952/http://www.educationforallinindia.com/1949%20Report%20of%20the%20University%20Education%20Commission.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1935年，成立印度兵工局（Indian Ordnance Service）管理全印度的国防工业。1947年印度独立前共有18家工厂。1948年IOS由国防部直接控制。独立后新建了21家工厂。1954年IOS改名为{{tsl|en|Indian Ordnance Factories Service|印度兵工厂局}}(IOFS)。 1962年在国防部成立了国防生产部。 1979年4月2日，OFB成立。 
 
